data.title: Grand Duke Paul Alexandrovich and Grand Duchess Alexandra Georgievna, when Princess Alexandra of Greece
data.meta_description: Photograph of Grand Duke Paul Alexandrovich (1860-1919) and Princess Alexandra of Greece (1870-1891), later Grand Duchess Alexandra Georgievna. Grand Duke Paul is sitting on a chair to the right, wearing military uniform and with a sword resting between his legs. Princess Alexandra is standing beside him to the left holding a closed fan. There is a large urn to the left and a small table to the right. There is a painted backdrop behind.Grand Duke Paul Alexandrovich was the youngest child of Alexander II,...
